    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Equipment that provides a means for passengers and aircraft personnel to traverse between aircraft doors and the ground or another surface outside the vehicle. These may be towed, self-propelled, or in some cases are integral to the aircraft.</Note_Text>
